  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. It's given that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"3 x minus 8 equals 7\"><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn></math>. Adding&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"8\"><mn>8</mn></math> to both sides of this equation yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"3 x equals 15\"><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>15</mn></math>. Adding <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"8\"><mn>8</mn></math> to both sides of this equation yields <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"3 x plus 8 equals 23\"><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>23</mn></math>. Therefore, the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"3 x plus 8\"><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"23\"><mn>23</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect. This is the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"3 x plus 8\"><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>",
